create a Virtual Environment :- python -m venv myenv   # myenv is the name of the virtual environment.
activate your environemnt :- copy the path and paste to activate, for powershell - activate.ps1, for cmd = .bat

install fastapi and uvicorn server :- pip install fastapi uvicorn

to run the server :- go inside your directory of fastApi
command :- uvicorn main:app --reload